{"word":"G3919 - παρεισάγω - pareiságō - par-ice-ag'-o - Privily bring in","slug":"G3919","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρεισάγω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pareiságō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-ice-ag'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Privily bring in"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03C3;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B3;&#x03C9; - pareisago&#x0304;</b> - <i>par-ice-ag'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1521\">G1521</a>; to <i>lead in aside</i>, that is, <i>introduce surreptitiously:</i> - privily bring in."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3920\">G3920</a>"}]}